    d = deque(p)
    chances = 0
    curr = 0
    tot = 0
    while tot < m:
        if (d[0] + curr) % k == 0:
            p = (d[0] - curr) // k
        else:
            p = (d[0] - curr) // k + 1
        temp = curr
        while tot < m and d[0] - temp <= p * k:
            d.popleft()
            curr += 1
            tot += 1
        chances += 1
    return chances
